snippet.title: Seven Pirates H | Nintendo Switch Gameplay
snippet.description:
”Genkai Tokki Seven Pirates” has become H (Hyper) and is now available on Nintendo Switch! !!
The pirate girl “Parte” is on a voyage in search of her treasure.
By the monster son “Otton” who suddenly appeared wearing a bra
She is dropped into the sea.
